然性格不好，但是还是认真抚养我长大了。不知道万一她以后一旦出现任何精神上，身体健康方面，或是经济方面的困难该有谁能帮助她。但是一旦呆在她身边，很容易被她的情绪和掌控力代入，变得失去自由的行动力和长期忍受在精神暴力下。现在的我很痛苦，不知道该怎么面对她，不敢去见她，不敢听她的语音。 请求各位朋友帮帮忙，我该如何调整自己的心态面对她，以及，她这样的精神状况有没有变好的可能性，如果没有的话，我该如何在保全自己经济，精神和人身自由的情况下达到和她稳定的来往和照顾。"},"attached_info":"Cj4IhZOIr6XgqZIJEAMaCDE5NTAzNjc2IJCqs9AFMAA4qgJADHIINjgxODc2NjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"46 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f339b30ac8a67d2e28d18675eba8faa0_720w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1726582718.174914","card_id":"Q_666786197","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":666786197,"title":"如何评价肖央、宋佳主演的电影《祝你幸福！》？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/666786197","type":"question","created":1725978838,"answer_count":25,"follower_count":45,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,199566,226543,2228809,2390763],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IhZOIr6XgqZIJEAMaCTExMDQ1MjUzMiDWsYG3BjAAOC1ADXIJNjY2Nzg2MTk3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"45 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-737dd22e0b701836214b482f779a4bc5_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"14_1726582718.175084","card_id":"Q_655249268","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":655249268,"title":"为什么家长都喜欢公务员？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/655249268","type":"question","created":1715075060,"answer_count":225,"follower_count":312,"author":{"type":"peop